Robert D. ASWELL, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-0093 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. March 13, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of mandamus is dismissed for petitioner's failure to respond to this court's order of January 17, 2018.

LaROSE, C.J., and CASANUEVA and CRENSHAW, JJ., Concur.
